;; @param <num-y-rad> The y axis radius.
;; @param <num-start> The start angle in 0 to 360 degrees.
;; @param <end-num> The end angle in 0 to 360 degrees.
;; Draw an ellipse with optional <bool-fill> either 'true' or 'nil' (default).
